Please enable an Admin to remove the recommendation to configure the backup service from the Admin gadget.

The "Admin" dashboard gadget in JIRA 4.x says:

{quote}You do not currently have a Backup Service running. We strongly recommend you create a JIRA Backup Service. To enable backups please create a backup service.{quote}

Your [documentation|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Automating+JIRA+Backups], however, states:

{quote}For production use, it is *strongly recommended* to use [native database-specific tools|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Backing+Up+Data] instead of the XML backup service. The XML backup is not guaranteed to be consistent, as the database is not locked during the backup process.{quote}

